    <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Habit Tracker</title>
</head>
<body>
    
<br>Keep track of your habits everyday, and don't break the streak!<br>Enter a goal and motivation in and click Submit to create a new habit.<br><br><span class="fa fa-plus"></span> - adds one to your habit streak<br><span class="fa fa-trash"></span> -  deletes the habit
<br>ğŸ”¥ - is your current streak    

    <h2>Add A New Habit:</h2>

    <form style="margin-left: 5%;"  action="/addRapper" method="POST">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Goal" name="stageName">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Motivation" name="birthName">
        <input class="btn" type="submit">
    </form>

    <h2>Current Habits:</h2>
    <ul class="rappers">
    <% for(let i=0; i < info.length; i++) {%>
        <li class="rapper">
            <span class="goal"><%= info[i].stageName %></span>
            <span class="motive"><%= info[i].birthName %></span>
            <span class="addLike"><%= info[i].likes %></span>            
            <span id="add" class='fa fa-plus'></span>
            <span id="delete" class='fa fa-trash'></span>            
        </li>
    <% } %> 
    </ul>
    
    <script src='js/main.js'></script>
</body>
</html>
